data.description: Charming 2 bedroom Sparks Condo.  This home features oak style laminate flooring downstairs with a breakfast bar and a half bath downstairs.  Upstairs you'll find 2 bedrooms with a jack and jill style bath.  This home is a great starter home or investment property and features a garage, private patio and 2 2 storm/security doors. Be sure to check out the fancy oven with an air fryer stove. Easy to show!
